Jacques Varennes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Varennes 0 Jacques Varennes (September 6, 1894 – November 8, 1958) was French film actor who appeared in around seventy films during his career. He appeared in Maurice Tourneur's 1938 historical film The Patriot.
